接口 OnFileDownloadStatusListener

    public interface OnFileDownloadStatusListener
    OnFileDownloadStatusListener, use OnRetryableFileDownloadStatusListener can be retry when failed once
    文件下载状态改变监听器

    wlf(Andy)
